d":"ab646f2eb9798e6c0b2c6b633326508bafb78d48","tid":384512,"uid":72454,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T16:58:43.000Z","msg":"好多道德委員會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2dc4e7a632553cd1093394b3965b7d52f4a2421c","tid":384512,"uid":6073,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T18:42:14.000Z","msg":"四五歲果時去公園玩<br />\n奇怪做咩冇咩人<br />\n原來有班仆街仔係咁用BB彈槍射人<br />\n一入公園即勁比人射<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n果時唔識野 喺花糟執舊石丟鳩佢地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"60242242a8244ea9a9b5b59c4e3e4a34f686afc5","tid":384512,"uid":63734,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T18:45:23.000Z","msg":"公屋仔"},{"pid":"837ebb513cb7a5fc74b372069eff8b7d219b8c56","tid":384512,"uid":59835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T19:07:22.000Z","msg":"會唔會係雙非bb或者新移民先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ca265eac2c4a01874fb69225fae6001c8b6b9c2","tid":384512,"uid":64716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T20:01:00.000Z","msg":"作為一個氣槍撚，又係鐘情sinper收藏家， o既粉腸。<br />\n每次睇到呢o的新聞都會好撚火滾，擺明係博衰哂其他小心又安份o既玩家。<br />\n我真係讚成捉到呢o的撚樣拉去坐監之前，要被人狂掃佢3000飛重火力教訓一下。"},{"pid":"1d440793f421b29e07d6e28ca42cdd89f0d65f33","tid":384512,"uid":85163,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T20:03:16.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6d1fb79f641dc1f90662ceaffa453fde6ff1e7a0","tid":384512,"uid":40804,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T21:08:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>個b都幾撚廢，中一槍又話爆晒血</blockquote><br />\non9仔你夠膽就企定定比枝兩j既氣槍廿米外射<br />\n睇你爆唔爆"}]}